{"type": "article", "id": 9279, "title": "Nike Free Rift Sandal", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-07T07:16:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235035HX4df7OFwSMCkaVc.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tNikeLab 最近在 Air Rift 的基础上，更新设计，推出了全新的 Free Rift Sandal 系列鞋款，鞋子保留了 Air Rift 来自东非大裂谷设计灵感的经典纹理。配置了一体式TPU鞋面，Phylon 中底和  Free 六边形跑步鞋底，目前鞋子有黑白两种颜色可选。鞋子已经登陆 <a href=\"nike.com/nikelab\" target=\"_blank\">NikeLab 网站</a>，将于 5 月 28 日在北美市场正式发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235032uh0yR7lYLW1XNtve.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235033UimlBDtrkNZ6EbzP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235033O26CEyLTDr1smAvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235034EcQ4atJi5WTUnxdF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235034Cc2kNragywZPEB58.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235034SKRYyzM915PDIBCX.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}